      <title>NFL 球队老板将投票决定是否允许私募股权投资球队</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/nfl-owners-set-to-vote-on-letting-private-equity-invest-in-teams</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国职业橄榄球联盟 (NFL) 球队老板将投票决定是否将其球队股份出售给私募股权公司，此举有可能加入职业体育联盟吸引机构投资者的行列。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/nfl-owners-set-to-vote-on-letting-private-equity-invest-in-teams</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 13:20:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西班牙以国家安全为由，因担心奥尔班事件而取消对火车制造商的收购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/spain-quashes-bid-by-orban-linked-company-to-buy-train-maker-talgo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙拒绝了匈牙利 Ganz-Mavag Europe Zrt. 收购火车制造商 Talgo SA 的提议，称该交易可能损害其战略利益并威胁国家安全。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/spain-quashes-bid-by-orban-linked-company-to-buy-train-maker-talgo</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 13:14:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
